videos.description: Ike Obiagu gets a block that sets up a fastbreak dunk for Terance Mann as the Seminoles jump out to a 9-0 lead.
videos.headline: FSU block leads to fastbreak dunk

videos.description: Chris Koumadje is unchallenged on a missed 3-pointer which he slams home easily.
videos.headline: Koudmadje follows with putback dunk for FSU

videos.description: M.J. Walker races to the rim and throws down hard over Anas Mahmoud.
videos.headline: Walker rocks rim for Noles

videos.description: Ray Spalding controls a lob from Quentin Snider with one hand and jams the alley-oop for Louisville.
videos.headline: Spalding throws down one-handed oop for Cards

videos.description: Ryan McMahon fires a 3-pointer to put Louisville up 64-62.
videos.headline: McMahon gives Cards lead with 3
